-- Strict tradition: only the 15 unconditionally valid moods.
-- No existential import, no subaltern moods.

tradition Strict

proof Barbara
  every M is P
  every S is M
  ∴ every S is P

proof Celarent
  no M is P
  every S is M
  ∴ no S is P

proof Cesare
  no P is M
  every S is M
  ∴ no S is P

proof Baroco
  every P is M
  some S is not M
  ∴ some S is not P

proof Bocardo
  some M is not P
  every M is S
  ∴ some S is not P
